{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"18d3345b-d51e-4451-8ded-2512a09a9eb2","content":"Here are the MSBuild evaluation performance issues in this project:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Recursive wildcard glob** (EvalHeavy.csproj, line 9)\n```xml\n<AdditionalFiles Include=\"**\\*.*\" Exclude=\"**\\bin\\**;**\\obj\\**\" />\n```\n`**\\*.*` forces MSBuild to walk the entire directory tree during evaluation. This is one of the most expensive operations in project evaluation, especially as the repo grows. If you need specific files, use targeted globs (e.g., `*.txt`) or list files explicitly.\n\n---\n\n### 2. **File I/O via property function** (EvalHeavy.csproj, line 13)\n```xml\n<BuildNotes>$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))</BuildNotes>\n```\nCalling `System.IO.File.ReadAllText` during evaluation performs synchronous disk I/O on every evaluation pass (IDE reload, design-time build, restore, etc.). This blocks the evaluation thread. Prefer reading file content at build time via a target/task instead.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Deep import chain** (level1 → level2 → level3)\n```\nEvalHeavy.csproj → level1.props → level2.props → level3.props\n```\nThree levels of chained imports, each setting a single property. Every import adds file-open and XML-parse overhead during evaluation. These could be flattened into a single `.props` file to reduce I/O round-trips.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Issue | Severity | Fix |\n|---|---|---|\n| `**\\*.*` wildcard glob | **High** | Narrow the glob or list files explicitly |\n| `File::ReadAllText` in property | **High** | Move to a build-time target |\n| 3-deep import chain | **Low** | Flatten into one `.props` file |\n\nThe wildcard glob and file-read property function are the primary culprits — both execute on every evaluation, which happens frequently in IDEs.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"dda15dcf-da2d-41d1-bea0-f159ec2dfd1d","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me analyze all the MSBuild evaluation performance issues I can see in this project.","outputTokens":525,"requestId":"781D:18FB68:1DEF559:225E6E0:69F551BE"},"id":"bfc663fe-228d-4016-99ab-6f97d80a99ce","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:22:20.420Z","parentId":"89669d7c-1ca8-4af9-b720-ce7379ad7890"}
